          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thin transmission targets were prepared by vacuum",
                "evaporation of 99% pure melamine (C3H6N6) onto",
                "approximately 50 mug/cm2 thick Al foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors.  The accelerated lithium beam was directed",
                "normally to the target surface with the aluminum layer",
                "facing the ion beam.  With this configuration it was",
                "not necessary to put any stopper foil in front of the",
                "charged particle detectors, as the H peak was well",
                "separated from the C and N recoils."
              ]
            }
          ],
